config APP_CS_ROLE_REFLECTOR
	bool "Gateway acts as CS reflector (peer is the CS initiator)"
	help
	  By default the gateway is the CS initiator. Enable this to make the gateway
	  the CS reflector instead. The gateway stays the BLE central and still drives
	  ALL CS setup (capabilities, config, security) - that rule is non-negotiable;
	  the peer peripheral becomes the CS initiator and enables the procedures
	  (role-swap). Build the matching target with CONFIG_APP_CS_ROLE_INITIATOR=y.

source "Kconfig.zephyr"
